parameters: Girl Ect: Ahahaha! Come on, over here, over here!
Girl Ect: Yes, here's my hand!
Mage Relm: Don't you have any pride!?
Girl Ect: Alright, next it's Relm-san's turn to chase!

Mage Relm: It takes quite some courage to provoke this
genius...!

Clea: I heard you were frail, but seeing you running around
energetically puts my mind at ease.

Melos the Hole Digger: Lately, it seems like you're in good
spirits. But that doesn't explain why you left me all alone.

Clea: Please stay with me as much as possible, because
unexpected separations can happen.
Melos the Hole Digger: Thank you. I'll keep it in mind.
Girl Ect: Let's play with Papa and Clea-san too!
Melos the Hole Digger: Ah, today I'll be with you all day.
Girl Ect: Yay, then let's go, let's go--
Clea: Let's take it to the room.

Hole Digger Melos: Alright, I understand. It's my fault, but
I want you to bring me a healing leaf.

events.name: ドラゴンの討伐時に木の実を受け取らなかったときのイベント

parameters:
Clea (This is the walnut that Celis-san planted for me...
It's surprising how much it has grown in such a short time,
isn't it?)
Clea: Let me gratefully harvest it.

It seems that the tree has lost its magical power and we can
no longer expect any further harvest.
Young female explorer Ect: May I sit next to you?

Young female explorer Ect: I heard everything, including how
Papa betrayed the Adventurer's Guild for my sake.

Young female explorer Ect: Being used by Psema and how the
people from the guild are truly saddened by Papa's death.

Young female explorer Ect: Clea-san... I didn't know that
the person you were fighting against was my Papa.
Clea: No matter the reason, it is a fact that I killed him.

Clea: While I was saying such arrogant things, I think I was
also running away from Melos-san's death.

Young female explorer Ect: I really admire Clea-san. She's
like a reliable older sister that I look up to.

Young female explorer Ect: But no matter the reason, she is
someone who killed my beloved Papa, someone I despise.
Young female explorer Ect: ...That's my honest feeling.

Clea: When I became a avenger, I was prepared to be killed
by the dragon that was the target of my revenge.

Clea: Even so, in the middle of my journey, I was
overwhelmed by fear and forgot about everything, including
my hatred, and ran away.

Clea: Maybe Ect is feeling the same way now, confused and
running away because the target of her revenge was me.

Clea: Please come anytime, but no matter what happens, I
will never lose.

Young female explorer Ect: Because of the promise with
Papa...?
Clea: That's also true, but it's the same for Ect.

Clea: You are a vengeful person who hates me, but at the
same time, you are also a valuable junior in the
Adventurer's Guild.
Young female explorer Ect: We're the same, aren't we?
Clea: Yes, we are the same.

Young female explorer Ect: Once I find the answer... I will
definitely let you know.

Young female explorer Ect: Hehe, the way you were just
now... it reminded me a little of Papa.

Clea: As someone who lived for revenge... I should have
killed Ect, right?

Clea: I think I made a weak choice, but this was for the
best, right, Melos-san?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
実績 復讐者たちの夜明

Young explorer Ect: I still can't sort out my feelings.
Maybe I need more time... Please, tell me your story again.

Young explorer Ect: Hello! The excavation of the ruins isn't
progressing as quickly as I'd like... but I'll do my best!
Clea: It's been since we talked back then, hasn't it?
Young explorer Ect: Thank you for helping me back then.

Young explorer Ect: No, that's not it... Clea-san kept her
promise with her father rather than her beliefs.
Young explorer Ect: So, thank you very much.

Clea: I have lived as a avenger. It means being prepared to
kill and be killed.

Clea: But, even so... the promise I made with Melos-san took
precedence within me.
Clea: I think I am a weak human.

Young explorer Ect: But thanks to that, I, who am still
alive, was kept alive by Papa and Clea-san.

Young explorer Ect: You actually came here to invite me to
the front lines, right?

Young explorer Ect: But I wanted to go back because I had a
promise with Papa.

Clea: Yes, that's right. I reconsidered that I shouldn't put
myself in danger.
Young explorer Ect: I'm going to the front lines!

Young explorer Ect: I've been saved by Papa and Clea-san all
the time, but there's something I can do too. I can fight
too.
Clea: But the answer to me is still--

Young explorer Ect: It's a crisis for the Adventurer's
Guild, right? I should be able to fight while searching for
the answer to that.

Young explorer Ect: So I'll go talk to Agonia-san and fight
together with Clea-san and the others!

Clea (I'm the same... I've been fighting until today while
searching for who I really am)
Clea: As I thought, we're the same.
Young explorer Ect: Did you say something?

Clea: No, let's fight together to protect the Adventurer's
Guild.

Young explorer Ect: Yes! I absolutely have to protect the
places Papa loved!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
